{"tid":712580,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"難忘既夢","createTime":"2018-06-22T07:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T12:08:33.000Z","uid":6371,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d16b9bc4f895879bb8f5460d51ae3d86f58966ca","tid":712580,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:49:26.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲打近排都發過d好難忘既夢？ 惡夢又好 開心既夢又好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我琴晚就發左個夢，夢入面唔知點解我無啦啦殺左我呀哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲驚人知之後收埋左條屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後唔知點解有人問我呀哥去左邊果d 嚇到我賴屎 成個夢都驚到仆街，最後唔知做乜就醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實成件事都好唔合理 但我夢入面果陣真係完全唔知自己係發緊夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最後醒左成個人彈起身 即刻心諗：屌 好在係發夢 無殺到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d19347d46eb4d92a36c70970029586b421a0002","tid":712580,"uid":6371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T09:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf7b35afd62865e17f6e194525ed664c2a79ba4","tid":712580,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:51:21.000Z","msg":"全盛時期既連登係咪無人發夢"},{"pid":"2f6a41bd5a79ed71b1fa5f10632c285df41dab80","tid":712580,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:57:37.000Z","msg":"自首啦"},{"pid":"5351554138c89a9c6c672dff322b2b6a0a3da276","tid":712580,"uid":88323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:59:21.000Z","msg":"發夢同男朋友69互含<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67c09da4338f4b0705fdeac65212440115b4371","tid":712580,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5351554138c89a9c6c672dff322b2b6a0a3da276","tid":712580,"ui